{"tid":1156290,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"做搞手真係好辛苦","createTime":"2019-05-15T13:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T06:13:31.000Z","uid":207111,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"91e2a5cd83be141607e5455774da8fc33bcd43f4","tid":1156290,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"次次搞活動 約出街 搞手永遠係第一個出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出完聲 其他人可以當搞手無到 唔覆機<br />\n但係搞手就要追住問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />欠撚咗佢地咁<br />\n真係唔撚明 講句ok有幾難呀 唔得閒咪講底你幾時得閒囉 <br />\n簡簡單單約時間一分鐘可以傾完 最後約撚咗成個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時我會係度諗 如果呢個世界無人做搞手 你班仆街係咪一世都唔會出黎<br />\n覆機喇屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6823fdb87c623dbea76c9ba4e8e3fda8c1ca12","tid":1156290,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"用reubird 等佢地自己投咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4f7c1bd2ee595fc25ae8e9590eeb9787ab69ce","tid":1156290,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"其實佢地私底下約左唔預你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfd175e68b6f1e385cdcbc4ad2e332af11afd5b","tid":1156290,"uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:30:47.000Z","msg":"樓主搞咩活動多<br />\n我都係搞手，完全明白<br />\n起個搞手聯盟，一分鐘就商量嗮d節目<br />\n你話幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5416f0f1b99746f83a8628eb3fcd8bb99f763d1","tid":1156290,"uid":169905,"li